<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.4">
<l>cūrmayi lāya pēymulai cuvaittuc cuṭucara maṭucilait turantu</l>
<l>nīrmaiyi lāta tāṭakai māḷa niṉaintavar maṉamkoṇṭa kōyil</l>
<l>kārmali vēṅkai kōṅkalar puṟavil kaṭimalar kuṟiñciyiṉ naṟuntēṉ</l>
<l>vārpuṉal cūḻtaṇ māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart; we will worship at cool Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by water where flows the scented nectar</l>
<l>Of fragrant, blooming cone flowers in the uplands where blossom</l>
<l rend="indent">silk cotton [and] kino [trees] that stretch to the clouds,</l>
<l>The temple kept in the heart of him who resolved to kill Tāḍakā</l>
<l rend="indent">who was without virtue,</l>
<l>Having sucked the breasts of the demon who arose in cruelty,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] having shot fiery arrows from his deadly bow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
